oped helpers over expanding already-large functions.\\n- Add or update tests for behavior changes.\\n\\n## Safety Rules\\n\\n- Do not publish packages, create tags, or push release changes unless explicitly asked.\\n- Treat `src/index.ts`, `src/utils.ts`, `src/plugin.ts`, and `src/esbuild/index.ts` as load-bearing before refactoring.\\n- Do not silently change public CLI behavior or output contracts.\\n- Before finishing non-trivial changes, run the relevant build, typecheck, and tests.\\n```\\n\\nThis is intentionally small: it gives agents commands, boundaries, conventions, and release safety rules without trying to duplicate the README.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":39191,\"cached_input_tokens\":12160,\"output_tokens\":536,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":22}}\n",
