edicated date module that doesn't abstract `now()` — that's the whole point of the module. |\n| 00007 | String Sprinkles — `\"enterprise\"` in 4 files | med / 0.60 | Plan literal scattered across api/billing/jobs/ui. Next \"enterprise\" rule will diverge. |\n| 00009 | Concept Alias Drift — tenant/account/org/team/workspace | med / 0.58 | 5 files, 4 vocabularies for one concept. Agents will accidentally fork logic. |\n| 00010 | God File — billing.ts at 310 LOC | med / 0.50 | Just over threshold; flag, don't block. Split when 00004/00008/00011 fixes happen. |\n| 00012 | Duplicated Navigation Source — `/settings/billing` labelled both \"Plans\" and \"Billing\" | med / 0.57 | User-visible inconsistency; close call vs. block. Warn because no functional break — but fix before docs ship. |\n| 00013 | TODO Density — todo.ts at 424/1k LOC | med / 0.57 | Filename is suspicious — likely a scratch file. Triage or delete. |\n| 00014 | Route Metadata Drift — `/settings/billing` has 4 competing labels | med / 0.56 | Same root cause as 00012; bundle fixes. |\n| 00003 | Commented-Out Corpse (billing.ts:33–37) | med / 0.53 | Dead `legacyRefund` snippet in the very file that has the refund bug magnet. Delete to reduce noise around 00008. |\n| 00018 | Return Shape Roulette — `resolvePaymentResult` | low / 0.48 | Low severity but 0% key overlap between branches → callers will guess wrong. Worth a type before someone extends it. |\n| 00021/22/23 | Orphaned Destinations — `/account/subscription`, `/team`, `/workspace/members` | low / 0.46 each | Three unreachable routes; could be in-flight (related to 00009 alias drift) or dead. Confirm intent — don't silently ship. |\n\n## ✅ Ignore (5)\n\nLow severity, low agent_risk, no nearby coupling to a blocked finding.\n\n| ID | Charge | Sev / agent_risk | Why ignore |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 00015 | Docs-Code Drift — broken link `./setup.md` | low / 0.51 | Single doc link; cosmetic. |\n| 00016 | Weak test matcher in `creates an invoice` | low / 0.34